name: Big Sal (Dank Candy)
description: Big Sal is that best friend that’s also a big league ball breaker. There’s no frontin’ with Big Sal. Remember, it is what it is and it aint what it aint. So if you’ve got a friend that thinks their shit don’t stink bring in Big Sal to set ‘em straight. See more of my work on IG @losdemoniosamigos
